\caption{(Color online). Loss-dependence  of hollow-core anti-resonant triangular-core fibers on the thickness of the perfect matching layers with $ t_{1} =  t_{3} = $ 2.19 $  \mu $m and $ \lambda = $ 2.94    $\mu $m. Blue stars, red circles, green triangles represent the fibers (a), (b), and (c).\label{Fig7}}
